{"release_time": "2026-04-14T15:26:21+0800", "update_time": "2026-04-14T15:26:40+0800", "description": {"title": "豆瓣影视榜单列表", "subtitle": "最近热门动画", "source": "https://m.douban.com/subject_collection/tv_animation", "link": "https://m.douban.com/rexxar/api/v2/subject_collection/tv_animation/items", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "page_total": 1, "page_limit": -1, "item_total": null, "item_limit": 20, "page_count": 1, "sup_page_count": 0}, "extra": {}, "stats": {"movies": 20}, "movies": [{"comment": "在惨烈的“涩谷事变”结束后，东京沦为咒灵横行的废墟。五条悟因被封印而被剥夺一切权利，咒术高层趁机下达严酷指令：重启虎杖悠仁的死刑，并指派特级咒术师乙骨忧太担任执行人。\n与此同时，幕后黑手羂索开启了名为“死灭回游”的残酷生存游戏。这场游戏强制全国数以千计的术师在特定结界内互相残杀，旨在以此产生的巨大能量推动人类的“进化”。为了营救被卷入游戏的伏黑惠之姐津美纪，并寻求从内部破解狱门疆、释放五条悟的方法，虎杖与伙伴们毅然踏入充满未知威胁的结界。在混乱的战场上，他们不仅要面对古代术师的跨时空阻击，还要在不断变化的规则中寻找一线生机。", "rating": {"count": 18219, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 8.8}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928402160.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928402160.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36714178", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926147569.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926147568.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928858425.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930269166.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动作 动画 奇幻 / 御所园翔太 / 榎木淳弥 内田雄马", "title": "咒术回战 第三季", "type": "tv", "id": "36714178", "tags": []}, {"comment": "「流泪道别并不适合我们，因为下次再见时会很难为情。」\n在勇者欣梅尔一行人击败魔王后的世界中，与欣梅尔等人一同为世界带来和平、活了千年以上的精灵魔法使──芙莉莲。\n在面对寿命已尽的欣梅尔之死时，因落下的泪水与心中涌现的情感，踏上了「理解人类之心的旅程」。在旅途中，她与曾由过去伙伴海塔抚养长大的魔法使费伦，以及同为伙伴艾冉的弟子、战士修塔尔克结伴同行，一同朝向灵魂长眠之地前进。\n在旅程中，与各种人们相遇交流，并与狡诈的魔族与魔物展开战斗。有时平静温柔，有时无聊琐碎，有时激烈动荡，有时直击心扉……所有的一切、每一个瞬间，都一点一滴地堆叠成三人无可取代的珍贵回忆。而在这趟旅程的终点，究竟等待着他们的会是什么？\n魔法使资格测试结束后，他们三人将再度启程──", "rating": {"count": 14252, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 9.0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2925567021.jpg", "normal": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2925567021.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36829083", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2923924502.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2923924503.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929070141.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929472264.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 奇幻 冒险 / 北川朋哉 / 种崎敦美 市之濑加那", "title": "葬送的芙莉莲 第二季", "type": "tv", "id": "36829083", "tags": []}, {"comment": "少女小说家的高代槙生在姐姐夫妇的葬礼上，面对被亲戚们互相推诿的姐姐的遗孤·朝无法视而不见，顺势决定收养她。但是把侄女带回去之后，不善交际的槙生才发现自己不适合和谁一起生活。于此相对，不认生的朝面对“不像大人的大人”的槙生却也坦率的接受了。女王和如小狗般侄女就此展开了同居生活……", "rating": {"count": 7352, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 9.3}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2927616043.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2927616043.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36803607", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929508814.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929313553.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928733054.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929508815.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 动画 / 大城美幸 / 泽城美雪 森风子", "title": "异国日记", "type": "tv", "id": "36803607", "tags": []}, {"comment": "女高中生铃木的个性开朗、交友甚广、擅长察言观色，是班上的中心人物之一，她喜欢的对象是坐在自己隔壁的男同学谷，而谷的个性与铃木恰恰相反，他内敛沉稳、有主见、待人一视同仁。铃木一直无法鼓起勇气告白，直到某日一个偶然机会，两人放学回家时走在同一条路上，并因此牵起了手。之后两人相互倾诉对彼此的好感，并开始交往，而同学们虽然感到讶异，但也都很支持两人的恋情。", "rating": {"count": 7291, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 9.0}, "vendor_count": 1, "has_linewatch": true, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2926685404.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2926685404.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37134598", "episodes_info": "更新至11集", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929105164.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929105162.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929105159.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929780223.jpg"], "vendor_icons": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/f/frodo/88a62f5e0cf9981c910e60f4421c3e66aac2c9bc/pics/vendors/bilibili.png"], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 喜剧 爱情 动画 / 长友孝和 / 铃代纱弓 坂田将吾", "title": "相反的你和我", "type": "tv", "id": "37134598", "tags": []}, {"comment": "月落和亚晨是一对双胞胎兄妹，他们在一个与世隔绝的深山小村落里出生，被称为“分隔夜与昼的双子”。他们拥有获得特殊力量的资格，一场围绕他们的双使战斗也随之展开。\n双使是一种成对的存在，被人类冠以“幽灵”、“怪物”、“怪兽”或“异形”等各种各样的称呼。它们并非人人可见，各自拥有不同的外表、性格和能力。每对双使都有一个与之缔结契约的主子，而指挥它们的主子被称为“双使师”。\n许多大人在双胞兄妹开始懂事前就暗中操纵，试图夺取他们的力量，因此月落和亚晨在年幼时就被迫分离。本作故事以兄妹俩的重逢展开序幕。", "rating": {"count": 616, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 8.5}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929520460.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929520460.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37105643", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2931394380.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2931543837.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2931543836.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2931543835.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 / 安藤真裕 / 小野贤章 宫本侑芽", "title": "黄泉的使者", "type": "tv", "id": "37105643", "tags": []}, {"comment": "上伊那ぼたんは20歳の大学生。\n入った寮の歓迎パーティで寮長のいぶきにハイボールを飲ませてもらうと酔った勢いでいぶきに絡み始めて・・・?\n酔っ払いいちゃいちゃガールズコメディ開幕！", "rating": {"count": 0, "max": 10, "star_count": 0.0, "value": 0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2930550821.jpg", "normal": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2930550821.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37228800", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930558534.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930558533.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930558532.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930558527.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 / 佐久间贵史 户泽俊太郎 / 铃代纱弓 青山吉能", "title": "上伊那牡丹，酒醉身姿似百合花般", "type": "tv", "id": "37228800", "tags": []}, {"comment": "由白滨鸥创作的漫画《#尖帽子的魔法工坊#(#魔法帽的工房#)》宣布动画化~\n【故事简介】\n生活在一个偏远村庄的少女可可一直渴望成为一名魔法师，但是这个世界只有出生就是魔法师的人才能成为魔法师。在一次偶然事故中，可可不小心看到了魔法师奇弗利施展魔法的过程，发现了魔法的真相。于是可可便临摹起了自己还是孩童时一位自称魔法师的神秘男子卖给她的一本绘本，不料却用出了强大而危险的禁忌魔法，将自己的母亲与房子都变成了石头。发现了自己不小心将魔法真相泄露而返回寻找可可的奇弗利看到禁忌魔法所造成的惨状，决心将她收为自己的徒弟，解开「绘本」之谜，帮助她将自己的母亲恢复原状。", "rating": {"count": 455, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.1}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2930062095.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2930062095.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/35633676", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930066953.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930066949.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930066938.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930066927.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 / 渡边步 / 本村玲奈 花江夏树", "title": "尖帽子的魔法工坊", "type": "tv", "id": "35633676", "tags": []}, {"comment": "为求仙药线索，一行人抵达统治岛屿的怪物\"天仙\"之居城。\n欲从岛屿生还，死囚与处刑人已不得不携手合作。\n与此同时，幕府以\"山田浅卫门殊现\"为首，下令增派人员登陆神仙乡。\n其中竟可见与画眉丸素有渊源的石隐众之身影。\n正当画眉丸等人欲尽快寻得仙药逃离孤岛之际，天仙们却拦住了他们的去路——\n围绕仙药的争夺，即将迎来\"人类\"与\"天仙\"的全面对决——！！", "rating": {"count": 3651, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2927505297.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2927505297.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36464824", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930264769.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929189151.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930549571.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2930469958.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动作 动画 悬疑 奇幻 冒险 / 牧田佳织 / 小林千晃 花守由美里", "title": "地狱乐 第二季", "type": "tv", "id": "36464824", "tags": []}, {"comment": "1890年，一场世纪大赛“SBR”于美国举开。全长共6000公里，是人类史上第一场骑乘马匹横越北美大陆的比赛！为了拿下高达5千万美元（60亿日元）的冠军奖金，一群强悍的冒险家们正式展开了他们的争战！", "rating": {"count": 4670, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.5, "value": 9.1}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928250933.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928250933.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36449242", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2925475309.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2925475312.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2925475313.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2925475314.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 动画 奇幻 冒险 / 加藤敏幸 木村泰大 高桥秀弥 / 坂田将吾 阿座上洋平", "title": "JOJO的奇妙冒险 飙